<!--
  Template: Post-Purchase Review Request
  File: 04-review-request-post-delivery.mjml
  Category: receipt-invoice / post-purchase
  
  Purpose:
  Request product/service review after confirmed delivery to boost social proof and customer engagement.
  Warm, gratitude-focused approach to maximize review submission rate.
  
  When to send:
  - 7-10 days after delivery confirmation (allows time for product testing)
  - After "delivered" shipping status update
  - Post-purchase nurture sequence (email 2 or 3)
  - Only to customers who haven't left a review yet
  
  Personalize:
  - {{first_name}}
  - {{product_name}} or {{product_category}} (e.g., "skincare products")
  - {{order_number}} (optional reference)
  - {{review_url}} for "Share Your Feedback" CTA
  - {{product_image}} - hero flatlay image
  - Brand colors (#ffe6a7 primary, #fdfcdc secondary, #3e2723 text)
  
  Notes:
  - Marketing/transactional hybrid (review request after purchase)
  - Gratitude-first approach: "Thank you" before asking
  - Educational section: "Why Your Voice Matters" reduces friction
  - 3-point bullet list = clear value proposition for leaving review
  - Community building language: "strengthen our community", "skin-positive"
  - Works best 7-14 days post-delivery (sweet spot for fresh experience)
  - Avoid sending too early (product not tested) or too late (forgotten)
  - Can be automated via Shopify/WooCommerce + email platform
  
  Best practices:
  - Keep tone warm, never demanding or transactional
  - Make CTA obvious but not aggressive
  - Explain benefits of leaving review (education = higher conversion)
  - Provide support contact in case of issues (prevent bad reviews)
  - Segment: Only send to satisfied customers (use NPS or delivery tracking)
-->
<mjml>
  <mj-body background-color="none" font-family="Arial, sans-serif">
    <!-- Header/Thank You Section -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffe6a7" padding="20px 15px">
      <mj-column width="100%" background-color="transparent" padding="20px 15px">
        <mj-text align="center" color="#3e2723" font-size="26px" font-weight="bold" padding="10px 0">
          Thank You for Your Purchase!
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image align="center" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1747161894/uploaded-by-ai/an-aesthetically-pleasing-flatlay-of-skincare-products-arran.jpg" alt="Skincare Product Flatlay" width="500px" padding="10px 0 20px 0" border-radius="7px"></mj-image>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#6d4c41" font-size="16px" padding="0">
          We hope your new skincare products have arrived safely and are brightening your daily routine. Your trust means everything to us, and we’d love to hear about your experience!
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    
    <!-- Main Feedback CTA Section -->
    <mj-section background-color="#fdfcdc" padding="20px 20px">
      <mj-column width="100%" background-color="transparent" padding="20px 15px">
        <mj-text align="center" color="#4d342e" font-size="20px" font-weight="bold" padding="10px 0">
          How Was Your Experience?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#4d342e" font-size="16px">
          Your feedback helps us grow and inspires us to keep delivering self-care solutions you’ll truly love. If you have a moment, please leave us a review about your shopping and delivery experience!
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button align="center" background-color="#ffe6a7" color="#3e2723" font-size="16px" border-radius="12px" font-weight="bold" href="https://yourreviewlink.com" padding="20px 0">
          Share Your Feedback
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    
    <!-- Benefits/Social Proof Section -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="15px 15px">
      <mj-column width="100%" background-color="transparent" padding="20px 15px">
        <mj-text align="center" color="#4d342e" font-size="18px" font-weight="bold" padding="10px 0">
          Why Your Voice Matters
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="left" color="#333333" font-size="15px" line-height="1.6">
          <ul style="padding-left:15px;">
            <li>⭐ Guide new customers to make informed choices.</li>
            <li>⭐ Help us improve our products and customer service.</li>
            <li>⭐ Strengthen our community with your honest thoughts.</li>
          </ul>
          Every review—big or small—makes a real difference!
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    
    <!-- Aftercare & Community Section -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffe6a7" padding="15px 15px">
      <mj-column background-color="transparent" padding="20px 15px" width="50%">
        <mj-image align="center" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1747161894/uploaded-by-ai/a-beautifully-composed-image-showcasing-natural-ingredients-.jpg" width="200px" alt="Natural Ingredients" border-radius="7px"></mj-image>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column background-color="transparent" padding="20px 15px" width="50%" vertical-align="middle">
        <mj-text align="center" color="#4d342e" font-size="14px">
          If you have any questions or need tips for your skincare routine, our friendly team is always here to help. We love being part of your daily self-care!<br/><br/>
          Your choice means the world to us—every review and message helps us grow and create what matters most to you. Thank you for supporting our skincare community!
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    
    <!-- Social Section -->
    <mj-section background-color="#fdfcdc" padding="10px 0px">
      <mj-column width="100%" background-color="transparent" padding="20px 15px">
        <mj-text align="center" color="#6d4c41" font-size="14px">
          Join our skin-positive community for tips, sneak peeks, and exclusive offers:
        </mj-text>
        <mj-social align="center" font-size="15px" icon-size="30px" mode="horizontal">
          <mj-social-element src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1740061171/youtube-round-outlined.png" href="https://youtube.com"></mj-social-element>
          <mj-social-element src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1739470105/twitter-round-outlined.png" href="https://twitter.com"></mj-social-element>
          <mj-social-element src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1728425053/linkedin-round-outlined.png" href="https://linkedin.com"></mj-social-element>
          <mj-social-element src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1740061962/instagram-round-outlined.png" href="https://instagram.com"></mj-social-element>
          <mj-social-element src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1728426637/facebook-round-outlined.png" href="https://facebook.com"></mj-social-element>
          <mj-social-element src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1740062001/tiktok-round-outlined.png" href="https://tiktok.com"></mj-social-element>
          <mj-social-element src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dk79hhqvp/image/upload/v1740061496/pinterest-round-outlined.png" href="https://pinterest.com"></mj-social-element>
        </mj-social>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffe6a7" padding="10px 15px">
      <mj-column width="100%" background-color="transparent" padding="20px 15px">
        <mj-text align="center" color="#4d342e" font-size="12px">
          You are receiving this email because you recently shopped with us.<br>
          Need help? Reach us at <a href="mailto:support@yourskincare.com" style="color:#4d342e;text-decoration:underline;">support@yourskincare.com</a>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#bfa278" font-size="11px" padding="5px 0 0 0">
          &copy; 2024 Your Skincare Brand. All rights reserved.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>